{"tid":2152297,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁美芬：人大比DQ四議員機會 希望佢地「好自為之」","createTime":"2020-08-12T02:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T04:57:47.000Z","uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"fe61109fcde01d41b34148c0702c87ee9a1bd5d1","tid":2152297,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:05:17.000Z","msg":"2020-08-12 HKT 09:35<br />\n <br />\n全國人大常委會通過相關《決定》，第六屆立法會延任不少於1年，而第七屆任期仍為4年。基本法委員會委員、經民聯立法會議員梁美芬相信，有關決定是在憲制及現實之間取得平衡，亦確立了延任的合憲性，相信未來1年不會有司法覆核的不穩定因素。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬在本台節目《千禧年代》說，現時香港處於水深火熱，立法會必須立即處理民生事項，中央今次給予香港機會，讓香港社會冷靜，處理民生工作，認為應「做得幾多得幾多」。<br />\n<br />\n對於人大常委會的決定是否有損基本法莊嚴，梁美芬認為，人大常委會並非釋法，否則會在《基本法》第69條有解說。<br />\n<br />\n另外，她相信今次決定亦是給予被選舉主任裁定提名無效的4名議員一個機會，希望他們「好自為之」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543240-20200812.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543240-20200812.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf6jakGblTMbnvy6EODhsvCk%3D&h=7b6c1b42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543240-20200812.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=017ae21e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543240-20200812.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"014a62edff4922ed21de88aa8c261942c6ca6745","tid":2152297,"uid":174767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:07:13.000Z","msg":"如果直接DQ佢地4個,肯定打官司打到今年立法會唔洗開會~~"},{"pid":"d2b676f63e1971a308512ee0605d11bd50d844ce","tid":2152297,"uid":286897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:07:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53643244212f691e99c8bf81c768b17ec70891b7","tid":2152297,"uid":36901,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:08:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uwEB3Sd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%